Enlarged uncus, valve, and phallus of male genitalia of 
<taxonomicName authority="Xu, Melichar &amp; He" authorityName="Xu, Melichar &amp; He" authorityYear="2022" box="[835,1259,1802,1826]" class="Insecta" family="Sphingidae" genus="Rhodambulyx" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="57" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="xinyuae" status="sp. nov.">
