Brechlin, 2015
</taxonomicName>
, Thua Thien Hue, Vietnam (G–L); and 
<taxonomicName authority="Mell, 1939" authorityName="Mell" authorityYear="1939" box="[1149,1360,1838,1862]" class="Insecta" family="Sphingidae" genus="Rhodambulyx" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="57" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="davidi">
<emphasis box="[1149,1240,1838,1862]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="57">R. davidi</emphasis>
